high_descs: Go to the bath tub.
Pick up a rag from the bath tub.
Walk to the small white table to the right of the sink.
Place the rag on the table.
Go back to the bath tub.
Pick up a second rag from the bath tub.
Walk back to the small white table.
Place the second rag on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two rags from the bath tub on the small white table to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, the hang a right and walk over to the tub.
Pick up the leftmost black rag out of the tub.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the black rag on the small white dresser to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk back over to the tub.
Pick up the leftmost black rag out of the tub.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the black rag on top of the small white dresser to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two black rags to a small white dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the bath tub.
Pick up the rag  in the front of the bath tub.
Turn right and step right to face the small white table.
Place the rag on the small white table.
Turn left and step forward to face the bath tub.
Pick up the rag  in the front of the bath tub.
Turn right and step right to face the small white table.
Place the rag on the small white table.
anns.task_desc: To move two rags from the bath tub to the small white table to the right of the sink.
